18.0pt'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt'>            Graduating someone with a
ministry degree does not necessarily increase the number of personnel in
permanent ministry. Several factors contribute to significant attrition,
especially during the early years of ministry. &lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>KNOWING BY FAITH</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/ministry/preparation-for-ministry/knowing-by-faith/</link><pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/ministry/preparation-for-ministry/knowing-by-faith/</guid><description>&lt;style>
